SDL_Rect snake_head_rect = {snake_x, snake_y, snake_head->w, snake_head->h};
SDL_RenderCopy(renderer, snake_head, NULL, &snake_head_rect);
```
This code loads the "snake_head.png" image, creates a rectangle to represent the snake head, and renders it to the screen using `SDL_RenderCopy`.

Remember to add error handling and release allocated resources properly to ensure your game runs smoothly and efficiently.

